          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"build_energy_model\"><code>build_energy_model</code></h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Factory function that constructs a fully wired <code>EnergyModel</code> from a Stage 0\nVQ-VAE checkpoint path. This is the entry point used by the training notebooks.</span>\n<div class=\"language-python codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">core.energy</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">build_energy_model</span>\n<span class=\"n\">model</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">build_energy_model</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;checkpoints/vqvae.pt&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;cuda&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div></span>"
